  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>It has a well equipped gymnasium and swimming pool. There is also Spa service that combines the healing arts of ancient and modern technique drawn from both the East and the West. (12/07SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is located on Rama 9 Road next to the Royal City Avenue with its broad range of pubs.  Access to airport expressway is from Rama 9 Road or Dindaeng Road within 600 metres. Nearest subway is available at Rama 9 station.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Rooms are large and color tone is bright with light wood furniture. Bathrooms are dark granite and are in good condition. The rooms are equipped with all the amenities.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is a modern twenty four storey white concrete and glass highrise with ten storeys of parking and the rooms beginning from the eleventh storeys up.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The coffee shop is located on the lobby floor, open 24 hours. Daily, serving Thai and International buffet and A la carte menu. A cozy cafe also located on the lobby floor, next to the coffee shop performing a live and serving teas, coffees, cocktails and light snack menu. Open daily from 11.00 a.m. till midnight.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The lobby is large with high ceilings and grey granite floors. There is a separate group check in area which is part of the main lobby. The lobby has plenty of seating.</Text>
  </Description>
